a. Install and Run Selenium Server:
http://phpunit.de/manual/3.7/en/selenium.html

b. Run composer install

c. Run ./vendor/bin/phpunit to start Selenium Tests

To record tets:

Install Add-Ons in Firefox:
Selenium IDE: http://docs.seleniumhq.org/download/
Selenium PHP Formatters: https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/selenium-ide-php-formatters/ 


